{"tid":395832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英33歲肥婆誘姦男童 用體重壓住迫性交","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T00:05:08.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27f8b950697b285f22ecc28d227ce3ee03b2f4b8","tid":395832,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170911/large/1505097455_4d88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F1505097455_4d88.jpg&h=64fad929&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505019921_cfeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505019921_cfeb.jpg&h=d5f960fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170910/large/1505019910_77da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170910%2Flarge%2F1505019910_77da.jpg&h=734bccd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一名33歲孌童婦誘姦一名13歲男童，案情指孌童婦利用身形優勢把男童壓住施暴，受害人哭著拒絕，但由於不想傷害女性最終被「霸王硬上弓」，他對於第一次性經驗被如此奪走「感到憤怒」。<br />\n<br />\n案件在赫爾皇家法院（Hull Crown Court）審理，被告福克斯（Nicola Fox）夏初引誘受害男童到自己家中，稱想與對方「聊天」，但當男童想離開時，她就拉上窗簾關上門，將他推在床上。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官指：「她用自己的重量壓住他，撫摸他的胸口，之後脫去他下半身的衣物。」福克斯制服男童並強迫對方與自己做愛。檢察官續指受害人出聲拒絕：「他一度大哭，但她只是叫他不要哭，以討厭及攻擊性的口吻說出來，他感到懊惱、沮喪、尷尬。」<br />\n<br />\n受害人非常憤怒但未能反抗，檢察官稱：「他說他曾想過反抗她，但始於意識到自己是被一名女性襲擊，而他不想傷害她。」福克斯聽到此處在犯人欄內不斷搖頭。受害人在聲明中表示，事發後他的家人非常支持他，但事件已令他失去自信，社交上變得孤立。受害人未經人事，經此侵犯後「他無法想像未來的感情關係，因為這事嚇怕了他，他感到憤怒，因為被告奪走了他所有的初體驗，這是無法彌補的」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n福克斯承認自己與兒童發生性行為，法官稱受害人不想傷害她，「但你就以那種方式佔他便宜」，判她入獄4年。福克斯同時要登記入性罪犯名冊。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"85927c8c24f396fece7e1e96cc1a53cb44b83b67","tid":395832,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"好野 當然留俾樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ec7d9eaf961db0bfe6e6911891389832025e79","tid":395832,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"66歲下話"},{"pid":"8c555734e5e098aa76df3c3ffd33aed07802c1f9","tid":395832,"uid":104443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"比人強姦緊仲話唔想傷害女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係癡咗線，紳士風度唔係咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6507d82480ef0ca5794ff9bbf89566205baa6683","tid":395832,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"33歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac62c2a4844258439308ad08c4c8778e1885cee6","tid":395832,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e2b0d5196a36f176db9afa10aad633b51bc4f1","tid":395832,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"唔想傷害女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細細個已經咁識諗寧願比人姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72e37842d15028986915af4bb062606b7bbc6b2","tid":395832,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"有請女權人士全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2984f8ae33237e9001cfdfb0aa072ce9934aff","tid":395832,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一世陰影"},{"pid":"200a4e205feb4f1541c9339bb923788e38e724eb","tid":395832,"uid":771